snippet.title: Something Ate My Alien Trailer 2020
snippet.description:
The official trailer of our game "Something Ate My Alien" 

Buy it now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1047870?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=videos&utm_medium=launch-trailer

"Something Ate My Alien" is a 2D puzzle and digging adventure game being developed by RoKabium Games. The full game was released on Steam and other store fronts 18th June 2020. 

Avialble on Windows, Linux, Mac and Atari VCS.

Add Our Game to Your Steam Wish List today!
Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1047870?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=videos&utm_medium=launch-trailer

Website: http://www.somethingatemyalien.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RoKabiumGames
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RokabiumGames
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rokabiumgames/
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/something-ate-my-alien/479495
IndieDB: https://www.indiedb.com/games/something-ate-my-alien/
GameDev: https://www.gamedev.net/profile/250586-rokabium-games/

Music: Dark Powerful Cinematic Electronic by Fab Claxton (licensed via pond5.com )
Sound effects: www.pond5.com
